Caching recommendations.

If you use a proxy server for your app users then we recommend to cache content on your end relating to the endpoints listed below.

Remaining endpoints have customized content for each user/call. So not listed here endpoints needs to be called every time.

/nutrition/recipe
Recipes.
/nutrition/mealtype
Meal types.
/file/*
Media files. All media (videos, images) can be cached.
/program
List of programs. (Individual progam can not be cached.)

If our recommendations above are still not clear, please check the FAQs page where we have further explanations and detail.

If still unclear following this, please feel free to contact us at api [at] active8me.com
